 Question metafor network meta-analysis with multiple time points
In-Reply-To: <CAN7ux0VfDg8FC58bMbQ-sOfZrtUT82ohEnaT5Tzz3UD5KGjgAQ@mail.gmail.com>
References: <CAN7ux0Xuqw58oEJ5HOhjHyJZK8_J8Z-RzyzcpSJqpFnrZ4LJJg@mail.gmail.com>
 <AS8PR08MB919397F32EEE5868917ED36B8B222@AS8PR08MB9193.eurprd08.prod.outlook.com>
